articles.title: Countries with worst diabetes rates in world REVEALED (and America's position will shock you) - Daily Mail
articles.description: Our World in Data ranked Pakistan as the country with the highest rate of diabetes. However, despite scares about poor diets and sedentary lifestyles, the US and UK both ranked much lower.
articles.content:
Americans might get a hard time for their high-sugar diets, but the US isn't even in the top 50 worst countries for diabetes, a new survey has revealed.
